<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>404 - Page Not Found | Healora</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #203f6a 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: white;
    }

    .container-404 {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
      animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .error-icon {
      font-size: 120px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: translateY(0px);
      }
      50% {
        transform: translateY(-20px);
      }
    }

    .error-code {
      font-size: 120px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      color:#ffffff;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      margin-bottom: 35px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .button-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      padding: 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 15px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: white;
      color: #203f6a;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: white;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .suggestions {
      margin-top: 50px;
      padding: 25px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 15px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .suggestions h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .suggestions ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .suggestions li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .suggestions a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 15px;
    }

    .suggestions a:hover {
      transform: translateX(5px);
      opacity: 0.8;
    }

    .suggestions i {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 576px) {
      .error-code {
        font-size: 80px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 26px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .button-group {
        flex-direction: column;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container-404">
    <div class="error-icon">
      <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
    </div>

    <div class="error-code">Oops!</div>

    <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
    <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>

    <div class="button-group">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
        Return to Home
      </a>
      <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-secondary">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i>
        Go Back
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="suggestions">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="/">
            <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
            Home Page
          </a>
        </li>
          <a href="/contact">
            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>